uot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:180,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:180,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;[&amp;amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-3&quot;&gt;Our practitioners span the intersections between marketing impact, product and service innovation, and new capability building — all in pursuit of uncommon growth for CEO and CMO buyers. Whether&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;[&amp;amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-3&quot;&gt;it&#39;s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;[&amp;amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-3&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;launching a go-to-market campaign, designing a new digital product, or standing up an AI-powered service from scratch, Digital is the team that builds it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:180,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:180,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;[&amp;amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-3&quot;&gt;You will be&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;[&amp;amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-3&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;immerse&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;[&amp;amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-3&quot;&gt;d&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;[&amp;amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt-3&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;in this maker culture while giving you hands-on experience inside Prophet&#39;s AI Foundry, the team behind MAIA. MAIA is our next leap in AI — an&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;[&amp;amp;:not(:first-child)]:mt

&lt;h3&gt;ROLE: Associate&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;LOCATION: Berlin, Munich&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Great work starts with a great foundation. And that foundation lies in the hands of our Associates. They dive into every detail of the business, working to gain an understanding of our clients, their growth aspirations, and what drives their customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Associates work with everyone in the firm, collaborating with colleagues across the organization. On any given project, you’ll interact with clients, Partners, Designers, Insights Specialists, Content Strategists, and many others from our rich multidisciplinary bench. The Associate role is organized to cultivate a true understanding of our approach to consulting and develop the skills to get it done.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Associates make great work possible.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;YOUR DAY TO DAY&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
