&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on multidisciplinary teams to help answer key strategic customer, growth, and transformation questions, through brand, marketing, and digital strategies, for Fortune 500 companies.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help conduct primary and secondary&amp;nbsp;research and analyze data; engage in creative problem-solving sessions to formulate hypotheses&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share your point of view and present insightful and actionable recommendations to internal senior leaders and our clients&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to internal initiatives within the firm including IP development, marketing, training, and ongoing educational sessions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive Prophet culture at the local office level through events such as: class gatherings, office wide social outings, and holiday celebrations.  &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE LOOK FOR&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relevant experience: Postgraduate experience ideally with a leading business/management, brand, or digital strategy consultancy, or with relevant industry experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Well-developed critical thinking capabilities, problem solving skills, and creative thinking&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Superior communication skills, both verbal and written&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of, and passion for, business strategy, business models, brand, digital, and marketing strategy, and how they drive growth and commercial impact&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A curious mind with an unrelenting commitment to get to the answer, to test new approaches, learn new skills, and push others’ assumptions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confusion tolerance: comfort with ambiguity and the ability to adapt, flex, and change directions given client, project, and team circumstances, understanding the ever-changing business world&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with AI tools, AI strategy or implementation experience, and/or exposure to GenAI applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in German and English is essential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Prophet is an equal opportunity employer. We are committed to building a team that represents a variety of backgrounds, perspectives, and skills. All employment, promotion, and evaluation decisions are based on qualifications, merit and business need.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

