&lt;li&gt;Partner with creative and production team to ensure feasibility of design solutions and articulate design principles and guidelines for implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present and substantiate all creative work to internal teams including logos, visual identities and systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicating with senior team members to receive feedback and improve design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively maintain expertise in graphic design software packages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in new business efforts as requested.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
